data.description: Look no further than this amazing single story home with RV parking and a pool! The home features a spacious welcoming floor plan with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Home has been remodeled with new flooring throughout and plenty of natural lighting. Living area includes a cozy fireplace and kitchen fully remodeled with new cabinets and countertops. Includes a brand new AC as well! The backyard features a sparkling blue pool with brand new texture and pool equipment along with a huge bonus workshop. In addition, the home has upgraded Anderson windows and exterior doors throughout including Rolland roll up shutters on all windows and exterior doors. No HOA! Don't miss out on this amazing home!
